<L>__{191. the surprise night}
<A>__{wide, on the troubled ship, small yellow patches of light visible from the gun ports.}
<L>__{192. below decks night}
<A>__{the men are lying in their hammocks when, from somewhere outside, there comes an ungodly howling. it stops, then comes again, exactly human in its pitch. the crew look at one another. this is like no sound they've ever heard. the howling stops then comes again, from another direction.}
